  "text": "The total number of precursor cells BLBPϩ, Sox2ϩ, immature neurons DCXϩ, and cells in mitosis in P14 mice (PHisHϩ) were calculated using the physical dissector method adapted for confocal microscopy as described elsewhere [CITATION_1] . Confocal stacks of images were obtained using a LSM710 Zeiss confocal microscope with a 63ϫ oil immersion objective. Four stacks of images were analyzed per animal.",
